tika.dc.description:
Coming July 29, 2014, the new novel from Liane Moriarty, #1 New York Times–bestselling author of The Husband's Secret

"What a wonderful writer—smart, wise, funny." —Anne Lamott

Sometimes it's the little lies that turn out to be the most lethal. . . .

A murder... . . . a tragic accident... . . . or just parents behaving badly?
What's indisputable is that someone is dead.
But who did what ?
Big Little Lies follows three women, each at a crossroads:

Madeline is a force to be reckoned with. She's funny and biting, passionate, she remembers everything and forgives no one. She's just turned forty—forty?! Her ex-husband and his yogi new wife have moved into her beloved beachside community, and their daughter is in the same kindergarten class as Madeline's youngest (how is this possible?). And to top it all off, Madeline's teenage daughter seems to be choosing...
